<title>I miei lavori</title>

<style>
body {
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
margin: 0;
background: #f4f4f4;
}

header {
background: #111;
color: white;
padding: 60px 20px;
text-align: center;
}

header h1 {
margin: 0;
font-size: 40px;
}

header p {
font-size: 18px;
margin-top: 10px;
}

.button {
display: inline-block;
margin-top: 20px;
padding: 12px 20px;
